		<ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
			<li class="list-group-item"><p>A great place to start is by reading the Agile Manifesto. Scrum is a popular Agile software development framework which is a great approach when setting up a new team if there isn't already an existing way of working. Kanban is an evolutionary method for improving a team's agility, and works well when the team already has an existing way of working in place.</p></li>
							
